ice of Advancement at Chicago Office of Advancement at Peoria Office of Advancement at Rockford Office of Advancement at Urbana University of Illinois Foundation  Search for:    Registrar Home / Education / MD Student Services and Support / Registrar  Registrar tlowery1 2019-05-21T09:36:06-05:00 Registrar Welcome to the website for the UI College of Medicine Office of the Registrar (COM Registrar). The COM Registrar oversees student records for students at each of the regional COM campuses (Chicago, Peoria, Rockford and Urbana), as well as the registration and grading for students at the Chicago campus.  Information regarding records  and registration that applies to all COM students are listed below.  For information and services related to a specific campus, please see the contact for each of the Regional COM Registrar’s listed in the contact section, also listed below. COM Records and Registration Information General Registration Information Activate your Portal account / Establishing your NetID and EnterpriseID and passwords Registration Dates Grading System for the College of Medicine AOA Membership Selection Information Medical Student Performance Evaluation (MSPE) Quartile in Class Calculation Student Name Change Information Graduation with Honors Criteria Chicago Office of the Registrar 105C College of Medicine West 1853 West Polk Street (M/C 785) Phone: 312-996-8228 Fax: 312-996-8922 Chicago Registrar Website Peoria Academic Affairs Campus Registrar 1 Illini Dr Peoria, IL 61605 Phone: 309-671-8409 Fax: 309-680-8605 Peoria Registrar Website Rockford Student and Alumni Affairs Campus Registrar 1601 Parkview Avenue, Room A203 Rockford, IL 61107-1897 Phone: 815-395-5581 Fax: 815-395-5979 Rockford Registrar Website Urbana Student Affairs Campus Registrar 125 Medical Sciences Building, MC-714 506 S. Mathews Avenue Urbana, IL 61801 Phone: (217) 333-8146 Fax: 217-333-2640 Urbana Registrar Information  Chicago Registrar  Peoria Registrar  Rockford Registrar  Urbana 